index.title: Ronico Billy
index.description: Student in computer science at the University Paul Sabatier of Toulouse 👨‍🎓 and freelance in my spare time, I have a profile of Full Stack Typescript developer 💻. I am versatile and master the various stages of creating a web or mobile application. From understanding the needs of users, to frontend and backend development to deployment 🚀. In love with the strong typing proposed by typescript, the tRPC technology interests me a lot at the moment.
